   1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 
   0 &amp; 2 &amp; 0  \cr 
   3 &amp; 0 &amp; { - 1}  \cr 

 } } \right]$$ satisfies the equation<br><br> $${A^{20}} + \alpha {A^{19}} + \beta A = \left[ {\matrix{
